&gt;&gt; James: We watch her scribble on the pillows
and chalk like she was just doing this morning**

00:37:43.200 --> 00:37:45.180
&gt;&gt;Brooke: Morning.

00:37:45.180 --> 00:37:49.150
&gt;&gt;James: before we left.

