00:38:55.670 --> 00:38:56.670
You know.

00:38:56.670 --> 00:38:58.141
&gt;&gt; Brooke: Easy for him to say.

00:38:58.141 --> 00:39:01.490
Easy for a Chop Champion to say.Just whips
